To compile:
mvn clean install

To run:
java -jar target/GameOfLiveDemo-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT-jar-with-dependencies.jar 10 30 30 true < 30_30_glider.txt

First parameter is runtime in seconds, second and third parameters are rows and columns. They should match the input file contents. The fourth (optional) parameter determines if the visualisation should clear the screen for each cycle. (keeping the visualisation in the same place)


